            p What is Lorem Ipsum What is Lorem Ipsum? Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry's standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of
        div#content3
            h2.header_email Tell me, Whats better?
            p
                small Spend 35 minutes on the phone and no exact options.
                br 
                p or
                p 5 minutes, answer questions, ang get your paymment options.
        div#content4 
            div.image_container 
                img(src="https://image.flaticon.com/icons/svg/330/330716.svg", style="width:40%")
        div#content5 
            h4 Answer all the same questions you would over the phone in the comfort of your home. 
            br
            h1 What are you waiting for?
            br
            button.button(type="submit" name="submit" onclick="boton()")
                b GET MY PAYMENT OPTION
        footer
